In a bowl, whisk together the egg and milk. Stir in the spinach, water chestnuts, 1/4 cup Swiss cheese, pimientos, green onion, salt and nutmeg if desired; mix well. Transfer to a greased 1-qt. baking dish. Cover and bake at 350 degrees F for 25 minutes. Sprinkle with remaining cheese. Bake, uncovered, 5 minutes longer or until cheese is melted.